{
  "name": "Watch Function Test",
  "description": "Demonstrates wallet operations with watch functionality",
  "version": "1.0",
  "config": {
    "baseUrl": "http://localhost:3031"
  },
  "stanzas": [
    {
      "name": "introduction",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": [
            "# Watch Function Test",
            "",
            "This demo demonstrates wallet operations with automatic watch functionality:",
            "1. Creating wallets with initial funds",
            "2. Setting up watchers to monitor balances and UTXOs",
            "3. Transferring funds and seeing automatic updates",
            "4. Checking wallet balances",
            "",
            "We'll create two wallets for Jeff and Nancy, set up watchers, and perform transfers."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "jeff_wallet_setup",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": [
            "## Creating Jeff's Wallet",
            "",
            "First, we'll create a wallet for Jeff with an initial balance of 50 ADA (50,000,000 lovelace)."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "javascript",
          "content": [
            "jeff = await createWallet('jeff', 50_000_000);",
            "console.log(`Jeff's wallet created!`);",
            "console.log(`Wallet name: ${jeff.name}`);",
            "console.log(`Initial balance: ${jeff.balance} lovelace`);"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "nancy_wallet_setup",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": [
            "## Creating Nancy's Wallet",
            "",
            "Now we'll create a wallet for Nancy with a larger initial balance of 75 ADA."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "javascript",
          "content": [
            "nancy = await createWallet('nancy', 75_000_000);",
            "console.log(`Nancy's wallet created!`);",
            "console.log(`Wallet name: ${nancy.name}`);",
            "console.log(`Initial balance: ${nancy.balance} lovelace`);"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "setup_watchers",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": [
            "## Setting Up Watchers",
            "",
            "Now let's set up watchers to monitor their balances and UTXOs automatically."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "javascript",
          "content": [
            "// Watch Jeff's balance with custom formatter",
            "await watchBalance('jeff', (data) => `💰 Jeff: ${data.balance} lovelace`);",
            "",
            "// Watch Nancy's balance with default formatter",
            "await watchBalance('nancy');",
            "",
            "// Watch Jeff's UTXOs",
            "await watchWalletUtxos('jeff', (data) => `📦 Jeff UTXOs: ${data.utxos.length} total`);",
            "",
            "console.log('Watchers set up successfully!');"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "transfer_funds",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": [
            "## Transferring Funds",
            "",
            "Let's transfer some funds from Jeff to Nancy and see the watchers update automatically."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "javascript",
          "content": [
            "transferResult = await transfer('jeff', 'nancy', 10_000_000);",
            "console.log(`Transfer completed: ${transferResult.transactionId}`);",
            "console.log('Check the watch results below for updated balances!');"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "balance_verification",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": [
            "## Verifying Balances",
            "",
            "Let's verify the balances after the transfer."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "javascript",
          "content": [
            "jeffBalance = await getBalance('jeff');",
            "nancyBalance = await getBalance('nancy');",
            "jeffAda = parseInt(jeffBalance) / 1_000_000;",
            "nancyAda = parseInt(nancyBalance) / 1_000_000;",
            "console.log(`Jeff's current balance: ${jeffBalance} lovelace (${jeffAda} ADA)`);",
            "console.log(`Nancy's current balance: ${nancyBalance} lovelace (${nancyAda} ADA)`);"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "final_summary",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": [
            "## Summary",
            "",
            "We've successfully:",
            "- Created two wallets (Jeff and Nancy)",
            "- Set up watchers to monitor balances and UTXOs",
            "- Transferred 10 ADA from Jeff to Nancy",
            "- Verified the transfer with automatic watch updates",
            "",
            "The watchers automatically updated after each operation!"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "language": "javascript",
          "content": [
            "console.log('\\n=== Final Summary ===');",
            "console.log(`Jeff's wallet: ${jeff.name}`);",
            "console.log(`  Balance: ${jeffAda} ADA`);",
            "console.log(`Nancy's wallet: ${nancy.name}`);",
            "console.log(`  Balance: ${nancyAda} ADA`);",
            "console.log('✅ Watch demo completed successfully!');"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
